Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.13,0:00:37.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这本能够...\N{\rENG}That could have gone...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}变得糟糕很多的\N{\rENG}A lot worse. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.67,0:00:41.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也可能变得好很多的\N{\rENG}Could have gone a lot better, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.67,0:00:46.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我收到了你的留言\N{\rENG}Steven, I got your message. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.11,0:00:48.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文?\N{\rENG}Steven? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.11,0:00:49.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}发生了什么?\N{\rENG}What happened?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.41,0:00:51.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们赢了!\N{\rENG}We won! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是紫晶吗?\N{\rENG}Is that Amethyst? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.60,0:00:58.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...一切还好吗?\N{\rENG}Uh, what--what's going on? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.02,0:01:00.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你说出现了巨大太空手掌一类的东西\N{\rENG}You said there's some kind of giant space hand
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.52,0:01:01.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而你们可能都得死?\N{\rENG}and you all might die? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮! 你不会相信到底发生了什么!\N{\rENG}Connie! You're not going to believe what happened! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.66,0:01:10.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我该怎么开头呢?\N{\rENG}Where do I even start? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:10.37,0:01:12.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里真是疯人院一般啊!\N{\rENG}It's been a madhouse over here! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶! 闹够了没!\N{\rENG}Amethyst! That's enough celebrating! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文!\N{\rENG}Steven! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}爸爸!\N{\rENG}Dad! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.44,0:01:23.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}康妮 我得挂了 我保证我会打给你的\N{\rENG}Connie, I have to go. I promise I'll call you back. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.78,0:01:25.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}爸爸回来了! 爸爸回来了!\N{\rENG}Dad's back! Dad's back! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.55,0:01:28.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢! 感谢上帝! 你没事!\N{\rENG}Oh! Thank goodness! You're okay! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.82,0:01:31.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我看到太空船开始起飞 \N{\rENG}I saw the spaceship start to leave, 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后又坠毁在这里 然后我返回这里 然后--\N{\rENG}and then it crashed, and I came back, and--
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}恶! 你的眼睛\N{\rENG}uggggh! Your eye. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.52,0:01:36.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你没什么大碍!\N{\rENG}But you're okay! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.96,0:01:39.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想那些混蛋们根本比不上水晶战士\N{\rENG}I guess those jerks were no match for The Crystal Gems. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.96,0:01:42.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不可能 ! 她们超级碉!\N{\rENG}No way! They were superstrong! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你还是想方法打败了她们?\N{\rENG}But you were able to beat them back? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 她们实力碾压我们!\N{\rENG}No. They totally stomped us! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.97,0:01:49.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有个铁石英战士超级粗壮\N{\rENG}This warrior Jasper was super-beefy
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.00,0:01:50.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}直接把我砸晕了\N{\rENG}and knocked me unconscious. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后她们将我绑架上船\N{\rENG}Then they abducted me onto the ship
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.14,0:01:54.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为她们想带走我\N{\rENG}because they wanted to take me away forever. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.24,0:01:56.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}接着我们让飞船坠毁了 我也差点挂了!\N{\rENG}And then we crashed the ship, and I almost died! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.68,0:01:58.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们到底想拿你怎么样?\N{\rENG}What did they want with you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.71,0:02:00.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们认为我是妈妈\N{\rENG}They think I'm mom. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.32,0:02:03.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有-有更多的母世界宝石人会在找你?\N{\rENG}A-are more homeworld gems gonna come after you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.55,0:02:05.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我--呃...\N{\rENG}I--uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.49,0:02:07.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道 也许会?\N{\rENG}I don't know. Maybe? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.36,0:02:11.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我非常支持你并为你感到骄傲 \N{\rENG}Steven, I'm supportive and very proud of you, 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且我马上就会回来\N{\rENG}and I'll be right back. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一定要淡定\N{\rENG}Got to calm down. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.57,0:02:17.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的--\N{\rENG}Where's my--
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的放松CD在哪?\N{\rENG}where's my relaxing-music cd?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.60,0:02:20.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个?\N{\rENG}This one? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.71,0:02:25.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不是!\N{\rENG}Wrong one! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.17,0:02:26.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}暂停! 弹出!\N{\rENG}Stop! Eject! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.02,0:02:43.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在 康妮 千万别发疯啊 \N{\rENG}Now, Connie, please don't freak out, 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.09,0:02:46.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但一个巨大的激光手试图将我绑架到太空\N{\rENG}but a giant laser hand tried to steal me into space. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.03,0:02:47.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但它没得逞 它没得逞\N{\rENG}But it didn't. It didn't. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我回来了 而且目前一切安...好\N{\rENG}I'm back, and everything is f-fine...Now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.04,0:03:02.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯 康妮 有趣的是--我发现 \N{\rENG}Um, Connie, funny story--as it turns out, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}宝石人的数量远远超过我们的想象\N{\rENG}there's a lot more gems out there than we thought, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.61,0:03:08.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而我觉得他们想...杀了我?\N{\rENG}And I think they want to...Kill me? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 康妮 那-那个我留给你的信息\N{\rENG}Hey, Connie, that--that message I left you
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.43,0:03:20.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只是--只是个梦\N{\rENG}was--was just a dream. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.52,0:03:23.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 这糊弄不了她\N{\rENG}Eh, she's too smart for that. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 嘿 罗纳多\N{\rENG}Oh. Hey, Ronaldo. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你没听说吗?\N{\rENG}Didn't you hear? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杜威市长号召每个人回到沙滩市\N{\rENG}Mayor Dewey's calling everyone back into the city. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们现在可以回家了\N{\rENG}We can go home now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.15,0:03:48.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 我知道了\N{\rENG}Oh. I see. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.09,0:03:51.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你也是来这里沉思啊!\N{\rENG}You come up here to brood, too! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}沉思?\N{\rENG}Brood? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Yes, Steven. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.36,0:03:56.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那正是人们想让我们做的--\N{\rENG}That's just what people like us do--
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}默默承受 \N{\rENG}suffer quietly, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.97,0:04:01.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}担负起其他人无法担负的认知\N{\rENG}shouldering the knowledge no one else can bear. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.44,0:04:05.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你自己作为"异常"的爱好者 \N{\rENG}As an aficionado of "the weird"yourself, 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.17,0:04:08.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可能已经注意到大众害怕\N{\rENG}you've probably noticed ordinary people fear
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.04,0:04:11.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}冰冷 沉重的真相\N{\rENG}the cold, leaded anchor of the truth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这深渊可不是闹着玩的\N{\rENG}The abyss is no Sunday swan ride. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道! 我爸爸在知道真相后疯掉了!\N{\rENG}I know! My dad flipped out when I told him! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听起来很正常\N{\rENG}Sounds typical. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这是个非常好的提醒\N{\rENG}But it's a good reminder. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.86,0:04:24.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们所选择的路并不容易\N{\rENG}This is no easy path we've chosen here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}经常有...\N{\rENG}There are...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}牺牲\N{\rENG}Sacrifices. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看看下面那些人 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Look at them all down there, Steven. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.47,0:04:33.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是我们的使命 让那些简单的人\N{\rENG}It's our duty to let those simple people
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}过着简单的生活\N{\rENG}live out their simple lives
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.34,0:04:39.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}无需了解与我们为友的负担\N{\rENG}without ever knowing the burden of being friends with us. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}至少我们可以相互支持\N{\rENG}At least we can be there for each other. 
