Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗷 别呀!\N{\rENG}Aww, come on! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.26,0:06:42.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要抱怨 我们得开始清理残骸了\N{\rENG}No whining. We need to start cleaning up the debris. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.43,0:06:43.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴说的对\N{\rENG}Garnet's right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人类已经开始返回镇上了\N{\rENG}People are already coming back into town. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们得让他们远离沙滩\N{\rENG}We've got to keep them off the beach. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果任何人类有机会接触到宝石科技 \N{\rENG}If any humans got access to gem technology, 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们很可能会伤害到自己\N{\rENG}they could really hurt themselves. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.31,0:06:55.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许我们该一劳永逸的将他们拦在外面\N{\rENG}Maybe we should shut them out for good. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.18,0:06:58.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要知道 我们的确设置过围栏\N{\rENG}You know, we did once have a fence. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.28,0:07:01.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那再建个新的吧--带倒刺的那种!\N{\rENG}Let's get a new one--with barbed wire! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.97,0:07:04.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这次 让我们修个护城河\N{\rENG}This time, let's build a moat. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可以当...\N{\rENG}I could be...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}鳄鱼精!\N{\rENG}♪ The crocodile! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.82,0:07:08.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}爵士手\N{\rENG}Jazz hands. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.13,0:07:09.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么不呢?\N{\rENG}Why not?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你总是说你要成为鳄鱼精 \N{\rENG}You always say you'll be the crocodile, 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你从没做到过\N{\rENG}but you never commit. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也不用围栏\N{\rENG}No fence, either. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石～榴!\N{\rENG}Garnet! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文得能见到他的父亲和朋友\N{\rENG}Steven needs to see his father and his friends. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 我不用\N{\rENG}No, I don't! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.00,0:07:26.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不能总是放不下我人性的那部分\N{\rENG}I can't keep clinging to the vestiges of my humanity. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是时候严肃点了\N{\rENG}It's time I got serious. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 为什么你的通讯设备\N{\rENG}Steven, why is your communication device
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}播放那个音乐?\N{\rENG}playing that song? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.15,0:07:36.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是康妮的电话\N{\rENG}It's Connie trying to call me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我不能再与她见面了\N{\rENG}But I can't face her anymore. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.69,0:07:42.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么...你就打算永远忽视她吗?\N{\rENG}So...You're just going to ignore her forever? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.84,0:07:44.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是负责任的做法\N{\rENG}It's the responsible thing to do. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这可不容易 \N{\rENG}That's gonna be hard, 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为她正沿着楼梯走过来呢\N{\rENG}'cause she's coming up the steps right now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.53,0:07:48.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蛤?\N{\rENG}What?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦!\N{\rENG}Ohhh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.07,0:07:57.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你好...康～妮\N{\rENG}Hello...Connie. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文在家吗?\N{\rENG}Is Steven home? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.18,0:08:03.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他还好吗? 我只是非常担心\N{\rENG}Is he okay? I'm just really worried. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他一直不接电话\N{\rENG}He hasn't been answering his phone. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}发生了什么?\N{\rENG}What's going on? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.51,0:08:07.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...\N{\rENG}Uhh...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我不知道\N{\rENG}I-I don't know. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我没法理解你们人类之间的关系\N{\rENG}I don't understand your human relationships. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么...呃...\N{\rENG}So...Um...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.62,0:08:15.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}再见\N{\rENG}Goodbye. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文!\N{\rENG}Steven! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文!!\N{\rENG}Steven!! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文?\N{\rENG}Steven? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文!\N{\rENG}Steven! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你惹麻烦了?\N{\rENG}Are you in trouble? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有什么不对吗?\N{\rENG}Is something wrong? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我做错了什么吗?\N{\rENG}Did i do something wrong? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么你要躲避我?\N{\rENG}Why are you avoiding me? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我知道你在这里!\N{\rENG}Steven, I know you're here! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.07,0:09:02.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你为什么要逃避我?!\N{\rENG}Why are you hiding from me?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"我们还是不要继续做朋友了"?\N{\rENG}"I don't want to be friends anymore"? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文?\N{\rENG}Steven? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不能再跟你在一起了\N{\rENG}I can't be with you anymore. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我有着自己的使命\N{\rENG}I have a destiny. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当面跟我说啊!\N{\rENG}Say it to my face! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}说你不想继续当我的朋友啊!\N{\rENG}Say you don't want to be friends anymore! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果你能这么做--\N{\rENG}If you can do that--
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果你能这么做 我就不再烦你了\N{\rENG}if you can do that, I'll leave you alone. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而我只用回到没有朋友的日子\N{\rENG}And I'll just go back to having no friends. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.20,0:09:41.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但除非你当面跟我说 我是不会相信的\N{\rENG}But I won't believe it until you say it to my face. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么?!\N{\rENG}Well?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我仍然想做朋友啊!\N{\rENG}I still want to be friends! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 你的眼睛!\N{\rENG}Steven, your eye! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你到底遇上了什么?\N{\rENG}What happened to you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不希望你担心\N{\rENG}I didn't want you to worry about it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我都担心的一整天了\N{\rENG}I've been worried sick all day. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.55,0:10:08.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你以为我为什么要到这里啊?\N{\rENG}What do you think I'm doing here? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.24,0:10:10.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只是想保护你\N{\rENG}I just wanted to protect you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.14,0:10:10.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}打住\N{\rENG}Stop. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只要告诉我一切就好\N{\rENG}Just tell me everything. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.04,0:10:23.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么...青金石和铁石英在海底的某处\N{\rENG}So...Lapis and Jasper are somewhere underwater. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.59,0:10:27.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错 而橄榄石在飞船下坠的时候逃脱了\N{\rENG}Yeah. And Peridot escaped while the ship was coming down. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.42,0:10:29.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她可能在任何地方\N{\rENG}She could be anywhere. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.09,0:10:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那真是够消化一阵了\N{\rENG}That is a lot to take in. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你还好吗?\N{\rENG}Are you okay? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你呢?\N{\rENG}Are you okay? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你才是经历了这一切的人\N{\rENG}You're the one that's been through everything. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我至少能做到倾听\N{\rENG}The least I could do is just listen. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不能要求你这么做\N{\rENG}I can't ask you to do that. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想这样 史蒂文\N{\rENG}I want to, Steven. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想成为你宇宙的一部分\N{\rENG}I want to be a part of your Universe. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}崽子! 你在这啊\N{\rENG}Kiddo! There you are. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.44,0:10:50.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 嘿 康妮 用送你回家吗?\N{\rENG}Oh, hey, Connie. Do you need a ride home? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 爸爸\N{\rENG}Oh. Dad. 
